race.description: Congrats Trl Premiership Champs Gatton Hawks Hcp
race.comment: The consistent SUPER QUICK (4) has only missed a drum once in nine attempts over this seven-furlong journey and will be at peak fitness now fourth-up from the spell. Gets the services of gun hoop Wiggins in the saddle and should be right there when the whips are cracking. ARAMINTA (3) put back-to-back wins together before not being disgraced in town at the latest effort. Will find this task easier, gets some weight off with the claim and draws the inside marble. Ticks a few boxes. DON'T DISS AROUND (1) has a handy record at this circuit with a win and four placings from just six spins. Cannot be discounted lightly. FORT WILLIAM (5) loves this course and distance with a win and a second from two efforts. In the mix.
